snippet.title: Suikoden 3 Intro
snippet.description:
Okay this ain't much of a present lol, it's just the intro to Suikoden 3, my next main LP. I'll make another video that'll give more insight on how this LP will be structured. This LP should be my "coming of age" LP as I have a slew of new programs to work with for video editing, so quality is of the essence here. So please enjoy, comment, etc.
Let's Play Suikoden 3 should begin around the first of January IF both of my current LP's are done.
